Class ConstantPoolReader

java.lang.Object
com.ibm.wala.shrike.shrikeBT.ConstantPoolReader
public abstract class ConstantPoolReader extends Object
This class provides read-only access to a constant pool. It gets subclassed for each class reader/editor toolkit you want to work with.
